'''''Anlage''''' was a massive [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ship]] of the [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]].

==History==
It neared completion in the [[Orbital Shipyard 1321]] construction dock at [[Fondor/Legends|Fondor]] when the shipyard was [[Battle of Fondor|attacked]] by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. The vessel was destroyed when [[Yorik-et|coralskippers]] rammed the slipway where it was being worked on. It was important enough for [[Commodore/Legends|Commodore]] [[Turk Brand|Brand]] to identify it by name when reviewing footage of the attack.

